description: Two men, two Motorbunny BUCKs, but only one can emerge on top. Michale DelRay and Dante Colle are in a battle of wills to see who can handle the intense thrusting vibrations of the Motorbunny BUCK longer. The prize? Each other's bodies. These two hot and hung studs ride their Motorbunny BUCK's until their knees are shaking and their hips are quaking with pleasure in this endurance-based competition that has two winners, but only one champion.
title: Buck Club
